<br>
For shopping, they have a well done search engine with multiple ways to filter to find the item(s) that fit your needs. Once you find the item you can right click on the seller's name and it will guide you to them to make your purchase.<br>
<br>
From what I've seen of it it's easily the most well implemented feature of EQ and Horizons could do a lot worse for a market model.<br>
